---

<ApplicationLayout
  title="Wastewater Centrifuge: Silicon Wafer Case | Dolphin Centrifuge"
  description="Disc centrifuge replaces ultra-filtration at silicon wafer facility: DMPX-070 processes 50,000 GPD of silica grinding wastewater, delivering $1.28M in savings."
